Package: Birdie
Title: Tools for Simple Data Analysis and Visualization
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Sophia", "Axel", email = "abs127@usf.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Birdie is an R package designed to make basic data analysis and visualization easier for students and beginner analysts. The package provides simple functions for cleaning data, generating summary statistics, and creating clear plots for exploratory analysis.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports: dplyr, ggplot2
License: CC0
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
